		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;Part-1&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Union and Its territories&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td&gt;Art.1 to Art.4&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
